<br>
i use a 33/22 1hs and a furious bash3 shield. even fully hasted there is no way i could hold aggro consistently in a group with just my melee damage.<br>
<br>
how in the world am i gonna hold aggro with just my melee damage when the rog across from me is doing twice the damage im doing? or the wizard whos doing 5 times the DPS im doing? a knight class will NEVER be able to keep up with that without casting.<br>
<br>
my stuns are a 1second cast and about an 18-20second recast. that means that for 2 seconds out of every 20, im not meleeing but creating insane hate. this makes my DPS drop from about 110~ish(tanking but not casting) to 100~ish(tanking but casting). this allows the rog's to not have to evade every chance it pops and it allows wizards to not waste time casting concussion/pacing thier nukes. my casting stun every chance it pops up can effectivly DOUBLE the DPS of the ENTIRE GROUP.<br>
<br>
please, come back soon for your next lesson in game dynamics.<br>
